  "body": "### Description\n\nWe have two use cases where we want to access the tenant-databases without coming from a http request. I didn't find any documentation on how to do it, so I'm not sure if this is just a request for a documentation or for the feature it self.\r\n\r\n1. We have some db-cleanup tasks running in schedulers. Therefor we need all the connections so that we can loop over them and inject them to the database services.\r\n2. We get events over mqtt and other messages buses where we use custom connectors. There we need a way to resolve the tenant per message.\r\n\n\n### Implementation ideas\n\n_No response_",
